Some people come to us with a romantic idea and fly in the clouds, and when they find out that they have to go to rehearsals twice a week, attend training courses and spend a lot of time on the road, they quickly lose their enthusiasm.
But this happens in any group that wants to work and achieve something.
The Tap Tap band currently has twenty members.
How many were there at the beginning in 1998?
Only one, Ladya Angelovic.
